fonttools: fonttools (A tool to convert True/OpenType fonts to XML and back)
fonttools:
fonttools: TTX/FontTools is a tool for manipulating TrueType and OpenType fonts.
fonttools: It is written in Python and has a BSD-style, open-source license. TTX
fonttools: can dump TrueType and OpenType fonts to an XML-based text format and
fonttools: vice versa.
fonttools:
fonttools: http://sourceforge.net/projects/fonttools/
